<h1 id=3D"id-04.SD:RefactoringSPA/MFE'stobeusedinOpenFin[ERM25E2February202=
5]-Solution"><span>Solution</span></h1>
<h2 id=3D"id-04.SD:RefactoringSPA/MFE'stobeusedinOpenFin[ERM25E2February202=
5]-SolutionOverview"><span>Solution Overview</span></h2>
<p><br></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable">
<colgroup class=3D"">
<col class=3D"">
<col class=3D"">
<col class=3D"">
</colgroup>
<tbody class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Feature</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Steps</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Details</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Adding OpenFin SDK to Galaxy SPA</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>Importing OpenFin Package</li>
</ul></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ol>
<li>Add OpenFin package to&nbsp;<code>package.json</code> of all MFE's / SP=
A</li>
<li>Import in <code>index.js</code>&nbsp; or `<span style=3D"color: rgb(23,=
43,77);">App.jsx`</span></li>
<li>Bootstrap so the package stars on start-up of the application (needed f=
or Session mgt)</li>
</ol></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><a href=3D"/display/WDVFY24/Multiverse-common+AP=
I">Multiverse-common API</a></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Making the SPA OpenFin aware:<br>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>Hiding headers and footers</li>
</ul></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<ol>
<li>For this, we will use the OpenFin method: <code>isCompositeDesktop(): P=
romise&lt;boolean&gt;</code>&nbsp;</li>
<li><code><span>The</span>/src/layouts/Master/MasterLayout.js</code>&nbsp; =
in the SPA application, has the following props=20
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">MasterLa=
yout.propTypes =3D {
  children: PropTypes.element.isRequired,
  withHeader: PropTypes.bool,
  withFooter: PropTypes.bool,
};</pre>
</div>
</div></li>
<li>In <code>App.jsx</code> , when the MasterLayout gets passed through (li=
ne 47), write code that overwrites the&nbsp;<p>withHeader and withFooter pr=
operties. Use the inverse value of <code>isCompositeDesktop()</code> ( use =
like !<code>isCompositeDesktop()).</code></p><br><br><pre><br></pre>&nbsp;<=
pre><br><br></pre></li>
</ol>
<p><br></p>
</div></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><!--
  ~ Copyright (c) 2014 by Mibex Software GmbH, Zurich, Switzerland.
  ~
  ~ All rights reserved.
