  ~ This product is the proprietary and sole property of Mibex Software Gmb=
H.=20
  ~ Use, duplication or dissemination is forbidden and is subject to prior=
=20
  ~ written consent of Mibex Software GmbH (office@mibex.ch).
  --></p>
<div class=3D"aui-message-container">
<div class=3D"aui-message aui-message-error">
<p class=3D"title"><strong>An error occured</strong></p>
<p>The Bitbucket resource could not be found. Check the file path provided =
and if the resource is from a private repo, ensure you have access. The Inc=
lude Bitbucket configuration may need to be reviewed. <a href=3D"$req.conte=
xtPath/contactadministrators.action" target=3D"_blank"> Contact your system=
 administrator. </a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p></p>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Enable OpenFin Navigation (=3D defining the d=
ifferent applications)</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>Define which apps needs to be 'registered' in Ping and Openfin.</li>
</ul></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong>Account MFE:&nbsp;</strong></p>
<ol>
<li style=3D"list-style-type: none;">
<ol>
<li><strong>Account Listing</strong> Application - <u>singleton</u>: <code>=
/galaxy/account</code>&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>Account Activity</strong>: Application <code>/galaxy/account/ac=
count-activity</code>&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>Transaction Detail</strong>: Application <code>/galaxy/account/=
account-activity/transaction-detail</code>&nbsp;</li>
</ol></li>
</ol><p><strong>Payment MFE:&nbsp;</strong></p>
<ol>
<li style=3D"list-style-type: none;">&nbsp;=20
<ol>
<li><strong>Payment Listing </strong>Application - <u>singleton</u>: <code>=
/galaxy/payment</code></li>
<li><strong>Payment Details</strong> Application: <code>/galaxy/payment/pay=
ment-details</code></li>
<li><strong>Make A Payment</strong> Application - <u>singleton</u>: <code>/=
galaxy/payment/make-payment</code>&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>Transfer Funds</strong> Application - <u>singleton</u>: <code>/=
payment/transfer-funds</code>&nbsp;</li>
</ol></li>
</ol></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>We will keep the SPA and MFE structure as is.=
 Openfin supports any URL as application.&nbsp;</p><p>The process for this =
is yet unclear</p></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Support Authentication through OpenFin</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Log-in authentication:&nbsp;</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>Is handled by Openfin Multiverse Navigator, because all our MFE's will =
share the same IDP (Ping) it will be a seamless experiences</li>
<li>Silent renewal stay as is&nbsp;</li>
<li>Inactivity renewal - TBD</li>
</ul><p><br></p><p>Log-out:</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>Is handled by Multiverse navigator. This will end the session in Ping f=
or all our applications.&nbsp;</li>
<li>Client side: our MFE's need to be able to receive the logout event, so =
we can clean the redux store</li>
<li>Openfin to handle the closing of the window</li>
<li>supposedly by bootstrapping the OpenFin package</li>
</ul></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">MFE's to be fully responsive design</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ol>
<li>Managed completely in the MFE UI - no further SD needed</li>
</ol></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Environment mapping</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><a href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au=
/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=3D1565918591" rel=3D"nofollow">W1C Dev/Test E=
nvironments - Master Environment Mapping - Maintained by JOHN KARALIS ONLY =
- Westpac One Core - Westpac Enterprise Confluence</a></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
